Package: IbssIss
Title: Assign Survey Positions for the Breeding Stock Survey
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "de Lestang", email = "simon.delestang@dpird.wa.gov.au",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Assigns observer positions from GPS coordinates to named locations
    in the Inshore Breeding Stock Survey (IBSS) and Inshore Survey (ISS).
    Provides polygon-based assignment using point-in-polygon testing and a
    nearest-centroid fallback for points that fall outside all polygons.
    Survey polygon data for all IBSS and ISS sites are bundled as package
    datasets.
